subject: Appointment of a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission
precis: Approval of the appointment by the Minister of State (Small Business and Tourism) of Darlene Brander of Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years.
